Several other things to modify from scratch Spark-1.6.1 downloaded from official website: 
(checked on Cluster)- in `Python.scala` of SQL module, modify the `compute()` 
- put the /conf in the correct position
- put the usage_pom.xml inside the spark/ main folder and replace the pom.xml there 
- copy the src directly into the target folder and replace the original one.


